creator: FieldForce
descriptionHtml:
GetFieldforce enables digital transformation of your deployment & operations.

Plan - Fieldforce helps you plan all deployment activities — from location identification to location acceptance. By digitizing every single data input on a consolidated platform, you get full visibility over supplier performance and project performance. Suppliers also get free access to your Fieldforce projects.

Manage - Fieldforce creates a central command post for all project activities and everyone involved. With everyone leveraging the Fieldforce platform, all stakeholders can collaborate in real-time. Management has full visibility over all activities happening across thousands of locations.

Analyze - Fieldforce digitizes your end-to-end deployment and operations process. Consistent data across all your projects, assets, and locations enables you to run analytics that wouldn’t be possible with any other system.
descriptionShort: All your field management challenges. One solution.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We regularly update the app so that you can have the best experience. This update includes following changes:
- Ability to update workflow against Not Started tickets.
- Ability to view ticket comments replies.
- Ability to view question level Manager Review Comments.

By digitizing every single data input on a consolidated platform, you get full visibility over supplier performance and project performance. Suppliers also get free access to your Fieldforce projects.

Manage - Fieldforce creates a central command post for all project activities and everyone involved. With everyone leveraging the Fieldforce platform, all stakeholders can collaborate in real-time. Management has full visibility over all activities happening across thousands of locations.

Analyze - Fieldforce digitizes your end-to-end deployment and operations process. Consistent data across all your projects, assets, and locations enables you to run analytics that wouldn’t be possible with any other system.
descriptionShort: All your field management challenges. One solution.
